description: Feel like homemade sausage rolls, only lighter? This tasty sausage roll recipe is bursting with hidden zucchini, carrot and parsley.
name: Healthier Pork & Fennel Sausage Rolls Recipe | Woolworths
recipeIngredient: 150 g mixed baby leaf salad mix

recipeInstructions.text: Brush top and sides of rolls with egg. Sprinkle with remaining fennel. Bake for 25 minutes or until golden and cooked through. Halve rolls, then serve with chutney and salad.
